<header>
    <p class="nav-back"><a href="/">&larr; W.D. Mo. Empirical Court Research</a></p>
    <h1>W.D. Mo. Bankruptcy — Filing Statistics & Case Patterns</h1>
    <p class="lede">Empirical filing statistics for the U.S. Bankruptcy Court for the Western District of Missouri: chapter distribution, monthly filing trends, and case volumes from publicly available PACER data via RECAP.</p>
</header>
<main>
    <div class="summary">
        <strong>4,485</strong> cases tracked &middot;
        date range: <strong>2025-04-23 to 2026-04-14</strong>
    </div>

    <h2>Chapter distribution</h2>
    <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Chapter</th><th>Cases</th><th>Share</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Ch. 7</td><td>2,259</td><td>50.4%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Ch. 13</td><td>2,192</td><td>48.9%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Ch. 11</td><td>28</td><td>0.6%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Ch. 12</td><td>6</td><td>0.1%</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Filings by year</h2>
    <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Year</th><th>Cases</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>2025</td><td>3,139</td></tr>
          <tr><td>2026</td><td>1,346</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Filings by month (last 24)</h2>
    <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Month</th><th>Cases</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>2025-04</td><td>145</td></tr>
          <tr><td>2025-05</td><td>350</td></tr>
          <tr><td>2025-06</td><td>355</td></tr>
          <tr><td>2025-07</td><td>428</td></tr>
