    </table>

    <h2>Methodology &amp; source</h2>
    <p>Cases compiled from the <a href="https://www.courtlistener.com/recap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RECAP Archive</a> via Free Law Project / CourtListener. Filing data updates incrementally as cases are added to PACER and mirrored to RECAP. Counts here may lag PACER by 1&ndash;14 days. For the source case index, see <a href="https://openbankruptcyproject.org/cases/ksb/">openbankruptcyproject.org/cases/</a>.</p>
    <p>Source dataset: <a href="/data.json">/data.json</a> &middot; License: <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CC BY-SA 4.0</a></p>
</main>
